# FileForge - Python File Handling Project

FileForge is a simple Python project that demonstrates basic file handling operations. It includes both a command-line version and a Streamlit web app version for creating, reading, updating, and deleting files.

## Features

- Create new files
- Read file content
- Update existing files
  - Rename a file
  - Append content
  - Overwrite content
- Delete files
- Streamlit-based user interface
- Stores app-managed files inside the `fileforge_files` folder

## Project Structure

```text
NYC-filehandling-main/
├── app.py                  # Streamlit web app
├── main.py                 # Command-line file handling program
├── spiderman.txt           # Sample text file
└── fileforge_files/
    └── hello.py            # Sample file
